block style 
  link(rel='stylesheet', href='../static/style.css')  

block content 
  section#introsection
    | Welcome to DanceFusion Academy
    div Eat Sleep Dance Repeat

  section#Missionsection 
    h2 Our Mission
    div.card
      h3 Dance Perfection
      div.card-box
        div.card-img
          img(src="/static/img/1.png", alt="logo")
        div.card-content
          p Every day brings a chance for you to draw in a breath, kick off your shoes and dance. 
    div.card
      h3 Dance the way you like
      div.card-box
        div.card-img
          img(src="/static/img/2.webp", alt="logo")
        div.card-content
          p I do not try to dance better than anyone else. I only try to dance better than myself.
    div.card
      h3 Expert teaching
      div.card-box
        div.card-img
          img(src="../static/img/1.png", alt="logo")
        div.card-content
          p Dance is a language beyond words, expressing that for which we have no words.

  section#sponsorsection
    h2 Our Sponsors
    div#sponsors
      img(src='../static/img/sp1.jpg', alt='SPimage', class='spImage')
      img(src='../static/img/sp2.jpeg', alt='SPimage', class='spImage')
      img(src='../static/img/sp3.webp', alt='SPimage', class='spImage')
      img(src='../static/img/sp4.png', alt='SPimage', class='spImage')
